{"tid":546055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聾協高層被指隱瞞賬目兼打人","createTime":"2018-01-31T07:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T08:19:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48cc21fff02d4c96095d85f5f28e6850e81f8732","tid":546055,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180131/20290905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F20290905&d=avymZ6sZwhxXJiMoodLcDeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=90abc709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F20290905&h=6b7c5b99\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180131/20290905</a><br />\n<br />\n聾協高層被指隱瞞賬目兼打人<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n       <br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180131/large/31ls3p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180131%2Flarge%2F31ls3p5.jpg&h=d816897c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港聾人協進會（聾協）前財務執委入稟高院，指控會長劉麗芳、行政總監吳應勇（圖）及諮詢委員會主席麥海華，於他任執委期間拒絕讓他審核財務資料，迫令或誤導他簽署文件。吳涉歧視聾人一度遭免職，惟吳帶人到辦公室毆打會員，事後劉與麥卻將吳復職，反終止被毆人士會籍，原告亦被終止會籍。<br />\n<br />\n原告陳家和透露他是聾啞人，成為聾協永久會員逾30年，2014年起任財務執委，被告為劉麗芳、麥海華、吳應勇及由劉和麥代表的聾協。陳指被告違反會章，威嚇侮辱他，又涉透過聾協的幼稚園謀取私利，要求法庭頒令被告交代賬目和賠償，並轉介律政司跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告入職9年拒學手語<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指吳入職9年來拒學手語，不少會員投訴吳行為囂張，感受侮辱和歧視。去年1月24日聾協執委會將吳免職。惟吳拒交出辦公室鑰匙，去年2月15日有人毀壞新門鎖，翌日吳違反禁足令現身聾協，毆打3名會員。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA246/18<br />\n■記者勞東來"},{"pid":"b36cf440243129972dc833f78d0734886f973584","tid":546055,"uid":107405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T07:23:39.000Z","msg":"唔英勇 名都衰過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228d849961bb5ff971af7d5927b14881f571aa17","tid":546055,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"識搵錢 社會精英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2ffc488f6f90db640a100515ea4bf039d97cce","tid":546055,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9db7591d3bfa4c2339839df6611b349b3f707e","tid":546055,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"228d849961bb5ff971af7d5927b14881f571aa17","tid":546055,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"識搵錢 社會精英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"有無心做野係另一件事，識玩遊戲先係人上人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}